{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ce0519d7a6","title":"首先歼灭锦塘段之敌","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ede3dafd46","index":0,"year":1948,"month":9,"day":21,"articleId":"ce0519d7a6"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji24","name":"毛泽东全集第24卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji24.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji24":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"6f6cff657c","type":"paragraph","text":"首先歼灭锦塘段之敌”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji24","articleId":"ce0519d7a6"},{"id":"76af024478","type":"paragraph","text":"（1948年9月21日）林、罗、刘按照近日北宁线敌情，甚有利于我军发展，望你们集中注意于该线之作战，首先达成歼灭该线（锦州至塘沽）敌军十九个师之目的。若此目的达成，则将来一切好办，否则将发生圈难","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji24","articleId":"ce0519d7a6"},{"id":"b3e7ed301d","type":"paragraph","text":"军委","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji24","articleId":"ce0519d7a6"},{"id":"25c8f9b2d5","type":"paragraph","text":"申马[1]这是毛泽东为中共中央军委起草的给东北野战军司令员林彪、政治变员罗荣植和参谋长刘亚楼的电最。[2]北宁线，指北平（今北京）至沈阳的铁路，即今京哈线一段。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji24","articleId":"ce0519d7a6"}],"page":{"id":"38b0089499","publicationId":"maoquanji24","articleId":"ce0519d7a6","start":482,"end":482}}}},"__N_SSG":true}